<plot>Set in the 1980's, a 12-year-old Israeli girl immigrates to the US because of the Israel-Lebanon war. In school she meets a Vietnamese refugee her age, and the two turn to each other for comfort, fun and guidance. As trust builds, the two mentor each other through their acclimation to life in the US and the beginnings of adolescence. When the friendship strikes turbulence, they must part with what they prize most, in order to gain something even better. Based on a true story.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?200520</url></doc>
